ClsGlobal.sSourceMnt = "/mnt/cdrom"
'ClsGlobal.sSourceMnt = "/mnt" &/ "source" 'FOR TESTING ONLY
'/ THE FOLLOWING LINES HAVE BEEN COMMENTED FOR TESTING ONLY
